name: React Labyrinth
description: React Labyrinth, a VS Code Extension, generates a hierarchical tree of React Components and identifies the component type with a single file upload.

name: Recipe Roulette V.2
description: Iteration of Recipe Roulette, a Recipe Sharing Application. Newly integrated user profiles with the ability to star favorite recipes, access nutritional labels, upload personal recipes, and search by ingredient.

name: Co-Sync
description: Co-Sync is a SCRUM app for cross-functional teams. Our goal is to help teams efficiently and seamlessly manage their projects and tickets through teamwork and collaboration.

description: Pet Health Online is a web application that allows you to view your pet's health records and vaccination due dates. Supports one-to-many relationships for owners and pets.

description: A simple Valentine's Day application to send to your friends and family.
